/F1 11 Tf 1 0 0 1 50 705 Tm (NeuroScan AI is a full-stack AI/ML web application for brain tumour detection from MRI) Tj
/F1 11 Tf 1 0 0 1 50 690 Tm (images. It combines a Streamlit frontend, authentication, SQLite database storage, image) Tj
/F1 11 Tf 1 0 0 1 50 675 Tm (preprocessing, deep learning prediction, Grad-CAM explainability, segmentation overlay, PDF) Tj
/F1 11 Tf 1 0 0 1 50 660 Tm (reporting, and dashboard analytics in one platform.) Tj
