/F1 11 Tf 1 0 0 1 50 630 Tm (intelligence can be integrated into a medical imaging workflow.) Tj
/F2 14 Tf 1 0 0 1 50 607 Tm (2. Problem Statement) Tj
/F1 11 Tf 1 0 0 1 50 588 Tm (Brain tumours can be life-threatening and require timely analysis. MRI scans are widely used) Tj
/F1 11 Tf 1 0 0 1 50 573 Tm (for tumour identification, but manual interpretation takes expert time. The goal of this) Tj
/F1 11 Tf 1 0 0 1 50 558 Tm (project is to assist MRI-based screening by building a system that can accept MRI uploads,) Tj
/F1 11 Tf 1 0 0 1 50 543 Tm (classify the scan, explain the model focus area, highlight suspicious regions, and generate) Tj
/F1 11 Tf 1 0 0 1 50 528 Tm (a report.) Tj
